# Decision sheet — access control

| Scenario | Pick |
|---|---|
| Analysts read gold | `USE CATALOG`+`USE SCHEMA`+`SELECT` |
| Block one table despite catalog grant | **`DENY`** |
| Hide PAN, show last-4 to fraud | **Column mask** |
| Compliance → their region's rows | **Row filter** |
| Mask/filter across 100s of tagged tables | **UC ABAC** |
| Non-UC client / very simple | **Dynamic view** (legacy) |
| Who read it last Tuesday? | **`system.access.audit`** |
| Column-level lineage | **`system.access.table_lineage`** |
| Production grants | to a **group** |